accessibility.text: The AlF3 coating does not influence the crystal structure of LiMn2O4, or the mechanisms of the lithiation and delithiation processes. Physicochemical and electrochemical methods were suggested to improve the electrochemical performances of LiMn2O4 materials, while the optimal quantity of thin-film AlF3 material on the surface of the LiMn2O4 material was found to be 2wt%.
AlF3包覆层不影响LiMn2O4的晶体结构，也不影响锂化和锂还原过程。提出的物化和电化学方法，提高了LiMn2O4材料的电化学性能，而LiMn2O4材料表面包覆的AlF3材料，其最佳(包覆)质量为2wt %。
